Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • Student
  • public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
    Student is the class for storing information about a student who wishes to attend prom. It contains the student's identification information, as well as preferred seating arrangements.
    Version:
    1.0, 02/14/10
    Author:
    Charles Wong, Cindy Wang
